I"±<p>The <code>blinkt</code> light platform lets you control the <a href="https://shop.pimoroni.com/products/blinkt">Blinkt!</a> board, featuring eight super-bright RGB LEDs.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To enable <code>blinkt</code> in your installation, add the following to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
light:
  - platform: blinkt
</code></pre>
